description:
Florida police arrest undocumented immigrant after a hit-and-run that kills a pregnant woman’s unborn baby. ‘House of Horrors’ parents plead guilty to torture, abuse, child endangerment, and more for tying up and starving their own children. A pair of Minnesota dogs call 9-1-1 over a dozen times.
